These are Puzzles for 7x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 7x2-Level-4-1::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, sprite
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: daffodil, aconite
2 different games are played: mah-jongg, backgammon
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: documentary, sports
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: march, april
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: swimming, volleyball
2 different pets are kept: hamster, guinea-pig
1. the person who growsaconite is on the left of the owner of the hamster##1
2. the person who's sport is volleyball is in an odd position##4
3. the person drinking sprite is on the left of the person playing mah-jongg##1
4. the person watching sports movies is on the left of the person who's birthday is in march##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |       2       |
| Beverage      | sprite     | hot-chocolate |
| Flower         | aconite  | daffodil       |
| Game           | backgammon   | mah-jongg    |
| Movie-Genre   | sports     | documentary   |
| Birthday   | april      | march     |
| Sport         | volleyball | swimming      |
| Pet     | guinea-pig       | hamster           |

