.:: Puzzle 7x2-Level-4-2::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: cola, sprite
There 2 different types of food: avocado, strawberry
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: weightlifting, snowboarding
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: adventure, romance
There are 2 different favourite colors: brown, fuchsia
The people have 2 different hobbies: puzzles, sudoku
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: indie, r&b
1. the person watching adventure movies is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the left of the person eating strawberry##1
3. the person watching romance movies is in an odd position##4
4. the person who likes fuchsia is on the left of the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
5. the person drinking cola is in an even position##4
6. the fan of r&b is on the left of the fan of indie##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |     2      |
| Beverage      | sprite         | cola       |
| Food          | avocado        | strawberry |
| Sport           | snowboarding | weightlifting    |
| Movie-Genre   | romance        | adventure  |
| Color   | fuchsia        | brown       |
| Hobby           | sudoku            | puzzles        |
| Music-Genre     | r&b            | indie       |

