.:: Puzzle 7x2-Level-4-3::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: coffee, water
The people have 2 different hobbies: reading, video-games
House: cape-cod, craftsman
City: rome, london
There 2 different types of food: cauliflower, banana
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: cycling, rowing
There are 2 different nationalities: japanese, spanish
1. the person who's sport is rowing is on the right of the person who's hobby is video-games##1
2. the person eating cauliflower is in an odd position##4
3. the person traveling to rome is on the left of the person drinking coffee##1
4. the craftsman house is on the left or right of the cape-cod house##3
5. the craftsman house is on the left of the japanese##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |
| Beverage      | water       | coffee     |
| Hobby         | video-games | reading    |
| House           | craftsman   | cape-cod |
| City   | rome     | london     |
| Food           | cauliflower     | banana      |
| Sport         | cycling     | rowing     |
| Nationality     | spanish  | japanese        |

