.:: Puzzle 7x2-Level-4-4::.
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: bolivar, dannemann
The people have 2 different hobbies: card-games, video-games
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: march, october
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: r&b, soul
City: edinburgh, hamburg
House: craftsman, art-deco
The people use 2 different means of transport: boat, van
1. the fan of r&b is in an even position##4
2. the art-deco house is in an even position##4
3. the person traveling to edinburgh is on the left of the person driving the boat##1
4. the dannemann-smoker is in an odd position##4
5. the art-deco house is the person who's birthday is in march##1
6. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the right of the person who's hobby is video-games##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |
| Cigar      | dannemann    | bolivar   |
| Hobby         | video-games | card-games |
| Birthday   | october      | march     |
| Music-Genre   | soul        | r&b        |
| City           | edinburgh        | hamburg |
| House         | craftsman    | art-deco |
| Transport     | van         | boat       |

