The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: mystery, romance
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: february, december
There 2 different types of food: cherry, broccoli
2 different pets are kept: lizard, rat
City: edinburgh, london
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: vegafina, game
1. the owner of the lizard is on the right of the person eating broccoli##1
2. the person watching romance movies is in an odd position##4
3. the vegafina-smoker is the person watching mystery movies##1
4. the person eating cherry is the person traveling to london##1
5. the person who's birthday is in december is on the left or right of the person traveling to edinburgh##3
6. the fisherman is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2      |
| Job           | journalist    | fisherman  |
| Movie-Genre   | romance       | mystery    |
| Birthday   | february        | december       |
| Food   | broccoli       | cherry    |
| Pet           | rat           | lizard     |
| City         | edinburgh | london |
| Cigar     | game    | vegafina        |

